Jonesy!

676
00:52:45.800 --> 00:52:48.360
- They're fucking cannibals. dude.
- Shut up.

677
00:52:48.400 --> 00:52:50.480
- Where the hell's the RV?
- Just over the ridge.

678
00:52:50.560 --> 00:52:52.920
- Keep quiet and keep moving.
- I ain't stoppin'.

679
00:52:53.000 --> 00:52:57.160
[Screams]
My foot!

680
00:52:57.200 --> 00:53:00.360
<i>- Let me look at it.
- I'm a shark. man. I gotta keep moving. or I die.</i>

681
00:53:00.440 --> 00:53:02.440
<i>- Shut the fuck up.
- You guys get to the R. V.</i>

682
00:53:02.520 --> 00:53:05.160
We'll be right behind you.

683
00:53:05.240 --> 00:53:09.440
- This is gonna suck.
- Oh. shit!

684
00:53:10.760 --> 00:53:13.320
I need to put pressure on that.

685
00:53:13.360 --> 00:53:15.480
- Come on. Give me your wristband.
- No!

686
00:53:15.560 --> 00:53:18.640
Look. you don't
have to hide anymore.

687
00:53:18.720 --> 00:53:21.320
How'd you know?

688
00:53:21.360 --> 00:53:25.280
When I found out I'd never play football again.
I spiraled down pretty hard.

689
00:53:25.360 --> 00:53:29.160
My therapist told me I should sit in
one of her suicide support groups.

690
00:53:29.240 --> 00:53:31.680
You know.
give me a better perspective.

691
00:53:31.760 --> 00:53:36.160
<i>There was a girl that used to do the same thing.
only she used a bandana.</i>

692
00:53:36.240 --> 00:53:40.320
- So how old is the scar?
- About six months.

693
00:53:40.440 --> 00:53:42.000
What happened?

694
00:53:42.080 --> 00:53:44.880
<i>I just trusted too many
of the wrong people.... All my life.</i>

695
00:53:44.960 --> 00:53:48.000
- But I'm past it now.
- So it's old news?

696
00:53:48.120 --> 00:53:52.120
[Winces]
Why do you think I came to win this game?

697
00:53:52.200 --> 00:53:55.720
Guess you'll get your chance
to do just that.

698
00:53:59.640 --> 00:54:02.240
<i>[Flies Buzzing]</i>

699
00:54:17.360 --> 00:54:20.160
<i>[Door Closes]</i>

700
00:54:29.760 --> 00:54:33.240
You so much as fart. old man.
and I'll drop you.

701
00:54:35.080 --> 00:54:38.320
Don't kill me. brother.
I'm a good Christian man.

702
00:54:40.000 --> 00:54:43.080
- Shit. Are you sure?
- Yeah. This was the place.

703
00:54:43.120 --> 00:54:45.800
Here are the tire tracks.
the empty equipment cases. the garbage.

704
00:54:45.840 --> 00:54:48.360
This is so f ed in the A.

705
00:54:48.440 --> 00:54:51.280
- [Gasps] The fucking RV. Is gone!
- Let's just keep going!

706
00:54:51.360 --> 00:54:54.120
- We're dead meat.
- Where to? The nearest town is 50 miles away.

707
00:54:54.200 --> 00:54:56.440
We're all gonna end up
hillbilly barbecue.

708
00:54:56.520 --> 00:54:59.240
- I'm not gonna tell you again. Keep quiet!
- Just come on.

709
00:54:59.280 --> 00:55:02.280
- There's that old paper mill out by the main road.
- It's abandoned.

710
00:55:02.360 --> 00:55:04.760
- We gotta dig in somewhere.
- Maybe there's a public phone.

711
00:55:04.840 --> 00:55:08.320
Dude. you know why they call it abandoned?
'Cause there's nothing in it. including phones!

712
00:55:08.400 --> 00:55:11.880
- Hey!
- Don't hurt me!

713
00:55:11.960 --> 00:55:14.880
That's a bear trap.
There's no animals around here.

714
00:55:14.960 --> 00:55:17.960
Why do they have
a fucking bear trap set?

715
00:55:18.040 --> 00:55:21.640
They're not trapping bears.
They're trapping people.

716
00:55:21.720 --> 00:55:25.720
There's no wildlife to eat around here.
They're eating us.

717
00:55:25.800 --> 00:55:29.360
Okay. I was wrong. Paper mill's a great idea.
Let's just get outta here.

718
00:55:29.440 --> 00:55:32.480
No. no. no. Look. man. if we take the road.
we're sitting ducks. all right?

719
00:55:32.560 --> 00:55:35.320
<i>So I want everyone to stick together
and watch where you step.</i>

720
00:55:35.400 --> 00:55:37.720
Yeah. no shit.

721
00:55:39.640 --> 00:55:41.560
Yeah.

722
00:55:46.120 --> 00:55:48.160
[Groans]

723
00:55:55.800 --> 00:55:57.960
[Groans]

724
00:56:00.600 --> 00:56:02.880
[Gasping]

725
00:56:06.840 --> 00:56:08.640
Who you blowin' up. old-timer?

726
00:56:08.720 --> 00:56:11.440
Oh. just the trout.

727
00:56:11.520 --> 00:56:14.600
Only way to bring 'em
to the surface.

728
00:56:14.680 --> 00:56:17.680
Dynamite stuns 'em.

729
00:56:17.760 --> 00:56:21.520
Then they float like lily pads.
and I just scoop 'em up.

730
00:56:26.880 --> 00:56:28.960
Pretty wife.

731
00:56:29.040 --> 00:56:33.960
<i>Yeah. that's my Delilah.
Gave me the happiest days of my life.</i>

732
00:56:34.080 --> 00:56:36.680
God bless her soul.

733
00:56:36.720 --> 00:56:39.920
<i>You know.
you one lucky son of a bitch.</i>

734
00:56:39.960 --> 00:56:44.320
<i>Lotta folk go in them woods.
Never seen one come out.</i>

735
00:56:44.400 --> 00:56:47.120
<i>I stay clear of them myself.</i>

736
00:56:47.200 --> 00:56:50.000
How many of those freaks
are out there?

737
00:56:50.080 --> 00:56:54.600
Hard to know. More than the ones
you run across. That's for sure.

738
00:56:54.680 --> 00:56:56.840
What are they?

739
00:56:56.880 --> 00:57:00.400
<i>Oh. just like you and me. brother.
'cept uglier....</i>

740
00:57:00.520 --> 00:57:02.440
and a lot stronger.

741
00:57:02.520 --> 00:57:06.120
Hey. I hit one of them young'uns
once in my pickup.

742
00:57:06.200 --> 00:57:09.320
He popped up and just kept goin'.

743
00:57:09.400 --> 00:57:12.440
<i>- [Groans]
- It's the chemicals changed 'em.</i>

744
00:57:12.520 --> 00:57:16.560
<i>Pulp mill shut down
near 30 years ago...</i>

745
00:57:16.640 --> 00:57:18.840
and left a mess.

746
00:57:18.920 --> 00:57:21.560
And the poison killed off
all the game.

747
00:57:21.640 --> 00:57:25.360
Most folks 'round these parts left.

748
00:57:25.440 --> 00:57:30.360
<i>There's one family
that stayed on in this holler....</i>

749
00:57:30.440 --> 00:57:35.120
<i>and pretty soon their babies started
gushin' out of their mama's womb....</i>

750
00:57:35.200 --> 00:57:38.800
just as ugly as them trout
I got hangin' out there.

751
00:57:38.880 --> 00:57:41.480
[Laughs. Mutters]

752
00:57:41.520 --> 00:57:45.600
And then they grow up.
have kids of their own.

753
00:57:46.960 --> 00:57:49.120
Turned out even worse.

754
00:57:51.240 --> 00:57:53.680
You gonna stay for a bite?

755
00:57:53.760 --> 00:57:57.160
Fish is ugly.
but they fry up real good.

756
00:57:57.240 --> 00:58:01.080
No. Much obliged.
but I gotta get goin'.

757
00:58:03.840 --> 00:58:07.920
<i>Well. if you're gonna head out
to get your friends. settle the score....</i>

758
00:58:08.000 --> 00:58:10.880
best jump to it before it gets dark.

759
00:58:10.960 --> 00:58:13.840
You don't wanna be out
in them woods at night.

760
00:58:13.920 --> 00:58:15.880
Why do you stay. old-timer?

761
00:58:15.960 --> 00:58:19.640
<i>Well. I could never leave.</i>

762
00:58:20.960 --> 00:58:24.280
Gotta stay close to my young'uns.

763
00:58:24.360 --> 00:58:27.080
<i>You motherfucker!
I gonna kill you. man!</i>

764
00:58:27.120 --> 00:58:29.960
[Shouts]
You killed my boy!

765
00:58:30.040 --> 00:58:33.240
[Shouting Continues]
I'm gonna kill you!

766
00:58:33.320 --> 00:58:36.080
<i>I'll kill you!
I'll kill you. motherfucker!</i>

767
00:58:36.200 --> 00:58:38.600
I'll kill you!
[Groaning]

768
00:58:38.680 --> 00:58:42.160
[Shouting. Muffled]
Motherfucker! I'm sure 'nough gonna kill you!

769
00:58:44.240 --> 00:58:48.560
<i>I'll get you!
I'll teach you to mess with my kids!</i>

770
00:58:57.920 --> 00:59:00.720
Say hello to the missus for me.

771
00:59:10.680 --> 00:59:12.600
<i>[Rifle Clatters]</i>

772
00:59:18.240 --> 00:59:22.320
<i>- [Woman Screaming. Grunting]
- [Man Grunting]</i>

773
00:59:28.640 --> 00:59:31.240
<i>[Screaming. Grunting Continue]</i>

774
00:59:38.040 --> 00:59:40.760
<i>[Nina]
It's one of them.</i>

775
00:59:45.760 --> 00:59:48.520
- It's Elena.
- Yeah? What makes you think that?

776
00:59:48.560 --> 00:59:51.800
- [Grunting]
- [Screaming]

777
00:59:51.880 --> 00:59:53.720
Hey!

778
00:59:53.800 --> 00:59:56.720
<i>[Screaming Continues]</i>

779
00:59:56.800 --> 00:59:59.160
Get off her!

780
01:00:01.480 --> 01:00:05.240
- Oh. my God.
- [Screaming]

781
01:00:05.320 --> 01:00:07.800
- Nina. wait!
- [Grunts]

782
01:00:10.240 --> 01:00:11.680
- [Grunting]
- Oh. shit.

783
01:00:17.960 --> 01:00:19.520
[Whimpers]

784
01:00:21.760 --> 01:00:24.920
[Panting]

785
01:00:27.920 --> 01:00:30.400
[Screams]

786
01:00:30.440 --> 01:00:34.200
[Shrieking]

787
01:00:42.080 --> 01:00:44.320
<i>[Jake]
Come on! Come on!</i>

788
01:00:48.000 --> 01:00:50.520
[Shrieks]

789
01:00:52.920 --> 01:00:55.680
- [Shrieks]
- [Neck Snaps]
- [Grunts]

790
01:00:57.880 --> 01:01:00.120
[Growling]

791
01:01:03.720 --> 01:01:07.080
Help me!

792
01:01:07.160 --> 01:01:10.080
[Whimpering]

793
01:01:13.120 --> 01:01:16.200
[Laughing. Sobbing]

794
01:01:16.240 --> 01:01:20.760
[Screaming]
Help!

795
01:01:21.880 --> 01:01:24.680
- Where's Nina?
- She deserted us.

796
01:01:28.600 --> 01:01:31.240
[Muttering]

797
01:01:36.920 --> 01:01:39.680
- Son of a bitch!
- Just keep moving.

798
01:01:41.600 --> 01:01:43.720
Look. split up.
I'll find Nina.

799
01:01:43.800 --> 01:01:45.760
- We'll meet up at the mill. Go!
- Okay.

800
01:01:58.160 --> 01:02:01.200
<i>- Nina!
- [Nina] Help me! Help me!</i>

801
01:02:01.240 --> 01:02:03.200
<i>- Nina?
- Help me!</i>

802
01:02:16.800 --> 01:02:20.040
<i>- [Jake] Nina?
- I'm.... Down here.</i>

803
01:02:20.080 --> 01:02:23.000
Nina? Are you okay?

804
01:02:23.080 --> 01:02:25.320
We gotta get you
out of there. all right?

805
01:02:25.360 --> 01:02:29.080
Look. come on.
Come on. Nina.

806
01:02:29.160 --> 01:02:31.280
[Grunting]
I can't reach.

807
01:02:31.360 --> 01:02:33.640
- Come on. Nina!
- [Whimpers]

808
01:02:33.720 --> 01:02:35.640
Almost.

809
01:02:35.720 --> 01:02:39.400
- [Grunting]
- Okay. hold on.

810
01:02:39.480 --> 01:02:42.240
- [Straining] I've got you now. I've got you.
- [Screams]

811
01:02:42.280 --> 01:02:44.720
- [Bone Snaps]
- [Groaning]

812
01:02:44.800 --> 01:02:46.640
<i>[Grunting]</i>

813
01:02:48.920 --> 01:02:50.320
<i>- Try a little right-
- [Grunting]</i>

814
01:02:52.320 --> 01:02:56.520
[Grunting. Panting]

815
01:02:56.560 --> 01:02:59.400
<i>- [Whimpers. Panting]
- What happened?</i>

816
01:02:59.480 --> 01:03:04.520
It's my shoulder. It's dislocated.
You gotta help me pop it in.

817
01:03:04.560 --> 01:03:09.160
Ah. no. Nina! Easy!
Okay. pull and twist. okay?

818
01:03:09.200 --> 01:03:12.440
<i>- Go. [Groaning]
- [Joint Snapping]</i>

819
01:03:12.520 --> 01:03:15.520
Help me up. Nina.
[Grunting]

820
01:03:15.600 --> 01:03:17.520
- It's like going to war.
- [Grunting]

821
01:03:17.600 --> 01:03:21.360
- Amber. Jonesy- Did they make it?
- We all made it.

822
01:03:21.440 --> 01:03:24.400
<i>- We'll meet up with them at the mill. okay?
- [Vehicle Approaching]</i>

823
01:03:24.480 --> 01:03:26.680
Let's go. Let's go.
Let's go!

824
01:03:31.600 --> 01:03:33.600
Come on. Nina.

825
01:03:48.960 --> 01:03:50.880
<i>[Gunshot]</i>

826
01:03:53.320 --> 01:03:55.360
[Giggling]

827
01:03:56.200 --> 01:03:58.240
- Let's go.
- Where?

828
01:04:05.560 --> 01:04:08.960
Shit! Shit! Shit!

829
01:04:36.280 --> 01:04:40.280
[Panting]
You-You totally kicked ass back there.

830
01:04:40.400 --> 01:04:43.560
I'm serious. You were. like.
Xena. Warrior Princess.

831
01:04:43.640 --> 01:04:46.240
You were right.
I was a total asshole before.

832
01:04:46.280 --> 01:04:49.360
I'm never gonna dis you
or any other female ever again.

833
01:04:49.440 --> 01:04:52.520
- Great.
- It's cool. We outran 'em.

834
01:04:52.560 --> 01:04:54.520
<i>- [Twig Snaps]
- Run.</i>

835
01:04:59.360 --> 01:05:01.240
Ow! Ow!

836
01:05:01.320 --> 01:05:03.680
- Come on.
- [Groaning]

837
01:05:04.960 --> 01:05:07.480
- Oh. shit.
- Come on!

838
01:05:08.720 --> 01:05:11.040
[Grunts]

839
01:05:12.120 --> 01:05:14.560
<i>[Grunts]</i>

840
01:05:16.560 --> 01:05:19.240
Just-There.

841
01:05:30.280 --> 01:05:32.840
Oh. my God!
[Screams]

842
01:05:32.920 --> 01:05:35.000
- Jonesy!
- Help me! Help me!

843
01:05:35.040 --> 01:05:37.840
Amber! Amber. help me!

844
01:05:37.920 --> 01:05:41.920
- Jonesy!
- Get me down! Get me down! Oh. no! Oh!

845
01:05:41.960 --> 01:05:45.720
[Whimpering]
Amber! Amber. help me!

846
01:05:45.840 --> 01:05:49.320
<i>Christ! Oh! Oh. God!
Hurry. Amber!</i>

847
01:05:49.400 --> 01:05:52.120
He's coming! He's com-

848
01:05:54.400 --> 01:05:57.800
- Amber? Amber. go!
- No!

849
01:05:57.880 --> 01:06:00.200
- Amber. don't do this! Get away!
- I'm not leaving you!

850
01:06:00.280 --> 01:06:03.440
Go! Run! No!
Amber. no!

851
01:06:03.520 --> 01:06:06.360
<i>Oh. God! Oh. God!</i>

852
01:06:06.440 --> 01:06:09.600
<i>- [Gasps]
- Amber?</i>

853
01:06:11.880 --> 01:06:14.440
- [Gasping]
- Jonesy!

854
01:06:14.520 --> 01:06:16.840
[Groaning]

855
01:06:17.920 --> 01:06:19.800
<i>- [Laughing]
- Jonesy!</i>

856
01:06:19.880 --> 01:06:21.920
<i>Give me your hand!</i>

857
01:06:25.360 --> 01:06:29.760
[Grunting. Laughing]

858
01:06:32.960 --> 01:06:35.440
[Mutters]

859
01:06:40.880 --> 01:06:44.800
[Laughing]

860
01:06:44.880 --> 01:06:47.560
- Huh?
- [Mutters]

861
01:06:47.640 --> 01:06:50.840
[Laughing]

862
01:06:53.200 --> 01:06:55.400
<i>[Amber]
Don't look down.</i>

863
01:06:55.480 --> 01:06:58.160
<i>[Jonesy Whimpering]</i>

864
01:06:58.240 --> 01:07:00.200
I'm here.

865
01:07:00.280 --> 01:07:02.640
Amber. I'm scared.

866
01:07:02.720 --> 01:07:04.800
<i>[Amber]
You're not alone.</i>

867
01:07:04.880 --> 01:07:08.400
All right.
I'm gonna get us out of here.

868
01:07:08.480 --> 01:07:13.360
[Gasps] You know. my mother
always used to say I'd live forev-

869
01:07:28.680 --> 01:07:31.560
<i>[Laughing. Slurping]</i>

870
01:08:00.640 --> 01:08:03.640
[Groaning]

871
01:08:10.400 --> 01:08:12.800
<i>[Groaning]</i>

872
01:08:16.480 --> 01:08:18.480
[Shouts]

873
01:08:35.800 --> 01:08:39.400
<i>- There it is.
- Jonesy wasn't kidding.
- [Drooling. Chortling]</i>

874
01:08:39.480 --> 01:08:42.720
This place is dead.

875
01:08:53.360 --> 01:08:55.640
"Birth defects."
No shit.

876
01:09:06.840 --> 01:09:11.480
Can't see anything. How the hell
are we gonna find 'em in here?

877
01:09:11.560 --> 01:09:13.640
Let Amber and Jonesy find us.

878
01:09:13.720 --> 01:09:17.080
- Where'd you get that?
- I brought it with me for the game.

879
01:09:17.160 --> 01:09:19.480
- I thought it might come in handy.
- That's cheating.

880
01:09:19.560 --> 01:09:21.520
Sue me.

881
01:09:26.880 --> 01:09:31.200
You think they're up there?
Maybe they found a C.B. Radio. called for help.

882
01:09:33.160 --> 01:09:35.760
I guess I'll go first.

883
01:09:37.760 --> 01:09:39.680
Be careful.

884
01:09:52.880 --> 01:09:57.320
<i>- They gotta be around here somewhere.
- [Picks Up Phone]</i>

885
01:09:57.400 --> 01:10:00.320
If they even made it here at all.

886
01:10:04.840 --> 01:10:07.360
Come on. guys.
Where you at?

887
01:10:10.320 --> 01:10:14.320
[Screams]
Oh. my God.

888
01:10:14.400 --> 01:10:17.160
<i>- She was just a little girl.
- Looks like she's been in there forever.</i>

889
01:10:17.200 --> 01:10:19.200
<i>- She's hiding.
- Yeah. but from whom?</i>

890
01:10:19.320 --> 01:10:22.200
<i>- This isn't right.
- [Vehicle Approaching]</i>

891
01:10:22.280 --> 01:10:24.440
- Nina. no! Nina! No. Nina!
- [Shouts]

892
01:10:24.520 --> 01:10:27.440
- Too late! We've gotta get out of here now!
- No! No. Nina!

893
01:10:27.520 --> 01:10:30.880
We cannot leave them. okay?
Let's go.

894
01:10:35.680 --> 01:10:39.480
Look. there's the RV.
I don't see 'em.

895
01:10:39.560 --> 01:10:43.040
Oh. Jesus. This family's
been doing this for decades.

896
01:10:45.680 --> 01:10:47.720
<i>[Man Screaming]</i>

897
01:10:47.800 --> 01:10:50.600
<i>Oh. my God!
That sounds like M. Screaming.</i>

898
01:10:50.680 --> 01:10:53.800
Okay. I'm going down there.

899
01:10:53.880 --> 01:10:56.920
<i>[Screaming Continues]</i>

900
01:10:59.160 --> 01:11:03.520
No. no. no. no.
Hold this.

901
01:11:06.160 --> 01:11:10.600
<i>- [Screaming Continues]
- Shit. You got my back?</i>

902
01:11:10.680 --> 01:11:12.960
[Grunts]

903
01:11:15.000 --> 01:11:18.600
<i>- [Michael] Somebody! Please!
- M? M?</i>

904
01:11:18.640 --> 01:11:22.040
<i>Come on. Come on.
Come on! Fuck!</i>

905
01:11:22.120 --> 01:11:24.040
<i>- Fuck face!
- M!</i>

